name: CABG_OpenAndEndoscopic
title: CABG_Open and Endoscopic
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This grouping of value sets identifies patients who have a CABG surgical procedure using open or endoscopic approach.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have a CABG surgical procedure using open or endoscopic approach.  Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Procedure category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only use codes which represent CABG surgical procedures using open or endoscopic approach.  Codes used are to be ICD10PCS, ICD9 or SNOMED-CT codes only.),(Exclusion Criteria: None.)
